title: Gloom Tribe
description: All Game Characters from the Gloom Tribe, the roles of Beasts, Archer, Swordman, Spearman, Barbarian, Mage, Brutal. Based on RK_Skeleton.
longDescription:
Here you can find all 96 members of the Gloom tribe.

Gloomclaw, Gloomheart, Gloomsoar, Gloomwind, Archer, Swordman, Spearman, Barbarian, Mage, Brutal


Includes animations common to all members of the Gloom tribe, as well as specialized animations of a Swordsman, Archer, Mage, Spearman, Barbarian, Brutal Knight.


Friends, are you looking for cool, juicy characters for your game? Roger Kint is looking for cool games for his characters !! Discord


Full Scene Preview

Content Preview

Animation Preview

Discord


Based on RK Skeleton.

All assets available in this and other packs and based on the RK Skeleton are compatible and interchangeable. You can rearrange body parts, add new ones - wings, tentacles, bodies, heads, tails, arms, armor, accessories, add additional animations.


  • 96 ready-to-use characters
  • 54 ready-to-use characters in armor: Skinny (2 options), Brutal (2 options), Damaged, Wings (2 options), Wings with Arms, Tentacles
  • 32 ready-to-use wild creatures with wings, tentacles, claws, fur and so on.
  • 10 ready-to-use clean bodies. For those who want to assemble their own warrior
  • Separate meshes for all parts of the body. Character body parts you can create new characters like in a constructor.It includes (each variant has 2 options - for a lean build and for a muscular build) - 4 torso variants, 2 head variants, 5 leg variants, 5 arm variants, 10 back options, 7 back options for wings, 7 tail variations, 3 wing variants, 4 tentacle variants
  • There are 6 skin colors represented for all elements of bodies and heads - Brown, Dark, Green, Grey, Red, Light.
  • 150 individual armors, 7 helmets, 5 shields, 5 swords, 4 axes, 5 spears, 4 cudgels, 1 bow, 1 staff
  • All armor, weapons and accessories have 4 types of materials - METAL for classic knight armor, GOLD for the armor of the king or leader, RUST for the brutal warrior who has seen many battles, DARK METAL for the warrior-antagonist-villain.
  • 4K Ultra high-quality PBR textures (metallic workflow)
  • Facial animation


468 Animations

4legs, Claw Attack, Sword Attack, Axe Attack, Spear Attack, Archer Attack, Mage Attack, Get Hit, Avoid, Fly, Run, Tentacles, Wings, Walk, Jump, Dart Attack, Death, Confuse, Scream, Turn, Stun, Shock etc.


Here you can find all members of the Gloom tribe individually:

Gloomclaw, Gloomheart, Gloomsoar, Gloomwind, Archer, Swordman, Spearman, Barbarian, Mage, Brutal


Competing tribes (also based on RK_Skeleton):

  • Ghost tribe - Ghostfang, Ghostfire, Ghoststorm, Ghosttail, Archer, Swordman, Spearman, Barbarian, Mage, Brutal
  • Obsidian tribe -Obsidianwing, Obsidianmoon, Obsidianfire, Obsidianclaw, Archer, Swordman, Spearman, Barbarian, Mage, Brutal
  • Dread tribe - Dreadfand, Dreadfire, Dreadflame, Dreadsilent, Archer, Swordman, Spearman, Barbarian, Mage, Brutal
  • Thunder tribe - Thunderfang, Thunderhowl, Thundermoon, Thunderstorm, Archer, Swordman, Spearman, Barbarian, Mage, Brutal
  • Night tribe - Nighthoof, Nighthowl, Nightstorm, Nightwhisper, Archer, Swordman, Spearman, Barbarian, Mage, Brutal
